reviewText: Arrived on time and as advertised!
I love this video!  Jim is an amazing teacher and I love his stories and sense of humor. I'm so sorry he's gone.

Excellent DVD, I highly recommend it is very didactic, not only for beginners but for professionals
I really like it, Thank you very much

This is an outstanding look at how mortise and tenon are made.  I had read Kingshott book on making tools and enjoyed it.  This was an introduction to him and his method of work.  You can watch it many times and pick up tips that you can't get from reading a book.
I really enjoyed it and will buy his other video.
